      "title": "실시간 파이프라인 흐름도 (문제 지점이 빨갛게 깜빡임 · 화살표 숫자 = 밀린 건수)",
      "description": "센서 → 수집 → Kafka → 정규화 → (DB적재 / 실시간전송) 흐름. 박스가 빨갛게 깜빡이면 그 프로그램이 멈춘/오류 상태, 화살표가 깜빡이면 그 구간에서 데이터가 밀리는 것.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 11,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "min(bridge_modbus_connected) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "sim_health",
          "refId": "sim_health",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(bridge_kafka_send_total{result=\"failure\"}[1m])) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "bridge_fail",
          "refId": "bridge_fail",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(up{job=\"kafka\"}) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "kafka_up",
          "refId": "kafka_up",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(streams_state) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "streams_state",
          "refId": "streams_state",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(dbsink_db_connected) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "dbsink_db",
          "refId": "dbsink_db",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max(kafka_consumergroup_members{consumergroup=\"factory-linestate-ws-backend\"}) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "ws_up",
          "refId": "ws_up",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(kafka_consumergroup_lag{consumergroup=\"factory-linestate-streams\"}) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "streams_lag",
          "refId": "streams_lag",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(kafka_consumergroup_lag{consumergroup=\"factory-linestate-db-sink\"}) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "dbsink_lag",
          "refId": "dbsink_lag",
          "instant": true
        },
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(kafka_consumergroup_lag{consumergroup=\"factory-linestate-ws-backend\"}) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "ws_lag",
          "refId": "ws_lag",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "content": "<div class=\"pipe\">\n<div class=\"node\" id=\"n-sim\"><div class=\"t\">① 센서<br>Modbus·MQTT</div><div class=\"s\">—</div></div>\n<div class=\"arr\" id=\"a-sim\"></div>\n<div class=\"node\" id=\"n-bridge\"><div class=\"t\">② 수집<br>KafkaBridge</div><div class=\"s\">—</div></div>\n<div class=\"arr\" id=\"a-bridge\"></div>\n<div class=\"node\" id=\"n-kafka\"><div class=\"t\">Kafka</div><div class=\"s\">—</div></div>\n<div class=\"arr\" id=\"a-kafka\"><span class=\"lbl\" id=\"l-kafka\"></span></div>\n<div class=\"node\" id=\"n-streams\"><div class=\"t\">③ 정규화<br>Streams</div><div class=\"s\">—</div></div>\n<div class=\"split\">\n<div class=\"branch\">\n<div class=\"arr\" id=\"a-dbsink\"><span class=\"lbl\" id=\"l-dbsink\"></span></div>\n<div class=\"node\" id=\"n-dbsink\"><div class=\"t\">④ DB적재<br>DbSink</div><div class=\"s\">—</div></div>\n<div class=\"arr\" id=\"a-ts\"></div>\n<div class=\"node\" id=\"n-timescale\"><div class=\"t\">Timescale<br>DB</div><div class=\"s\">—</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"branch\">\n<div class=\"arr\" id=\"a-ws\"><span class=\"lbl\" id=\"l-ws\"></span></div>\n<div class=\"node\" id=\"n-wsserver\"><div class=\"t\">④ 실시간전송<br>WsServer</div><div class=\"s\">—</div></div>\n<div class=\"arr\" id=\"a-br\"></div>\n<div class=\"node\" id=\"n-browser\"><div class=\"t\">브라우저<br>화면</div><div class=\"s\">표시</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
        "defaultContent": "데이터 없음",
        "renderMode": "data",
        "editor": {
          "format": "auto",
          "language": "html"
        },
        "editors": [],
        "externalStyles": [],
        "contentPartials": [],
        "helpers": "",
        "status": "",
        "styles": ".pipe { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:10px 6px; overflow-x:auto; }\n.node { min-width:84px; padding:9px 7px; border-radius:9px; text-align:center; color:#fff;\n        background:#2f9e44; border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.35); box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.25); }\n.node .t { font-size:12px; font-weight:700; line-height:1.15; }\n.node .s { font-size:11px; margin-top:4px; opacity:.95; font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums; }\n.node.warn { background:#f08c00; }\n.node.bad  { background:#e03131; animation: blink 1s steps(1,end) infinite; }\n.split  { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px; }\n.branch { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; }\n.arr { position:relative; width:54px; height:26px; flex:0 0 auto; }\n.arr .lbl { position:absolute; top:-13px; left:0; width:100%; text-align:center;\n            font-size:10px; color:#868e96; font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums; }\n.arr::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:11px; left:0; width:42px; height:4px; background:#2f9e44; }\n.arr::after  { content:''; position:absolute; top:5px; left:40px;\n               border-left:12px solid #2f9e44; border-top:8px solid transparent; border-bottom:8px solid transparent; }\n.arr.warn::before { background:#f08c00; } .arr.warn::after { border-left-color:#f08c00; }\n.arr.bad::before  { background:#e03131; animation: blink 1s steps(1,end) infinite; }\n.arr.bad::after   { border-left-color:#e03131; animation: blink 1s steps(1,end) infinite; }\n@keyframes blink { 0%,49% { opacity:1; } 50%,100% { opacity:.2; } }",
        "afterRender": "\nvar el = context.element;\nvar series = (context.panelData && context.panelData.series) ? context.panelData.series : [];\nvar V = {};\nseries.forEach(function (fr) {\n  var nf = null, fs = fr.fields || [];\n  for (var i = 0; i < fs.length; i++) { if (fs[i].type === 'number') { nf = fs[i]; break; } }\n  if (!nf) return;\n  var vs = (nf.values && nf.values.toArray) ? nf.values.toArray() : (nf.values || []);\n  var last = null;\n  for (var j = vs.length - 1; j >= 0; j--) { if (vs[j] != null && !isNaN(vs[j])) { last = vs[j]; break; } }\n  V[fr.refId] = last;\n});\nfunction up(v)   { return (v != null && v >= 1) ? 'ok' : 'bad'; }\nfunction stt(v)  { return (v >= 2) ? 'ok' : (v >= 1 ? 'warn' : 'bad'); }\nfunction fail(v) { return (v == null) ? 'ok' : (v > 0.01 ? 'bad' : 'ok'); }\nfunction lagc(v) { return (v == null) ? 'ok' : (v >= 500 ? 'bad' : (v >= 50 ? 'warn' : 'ok')); }\nfunction node(id, cls, txt) {\n  var e = el.querySelector('#' + id); if (!e) return;\n  e.classList.remove('ok', 'warn', 'bad'); e.classList.add(cls);\n  var s = e.querySelector('.s'); if (s && txt != null) s.textContent = txt;\n}\nfunction edge(aid, lid, cls, lagv) {\n  var a = el.querySelector('#' + aid);\n  if (a) { a.classList.remove('ok', 'warn', 'bad'); a.classList.add(cls); }\n  if (lid) { var l = el.querySelector('#' + lid); if (l) l.textContent = (lagv != null ? Math.round(lagv) + '건' : ''); }\n}\nnode('n-sim',       up(V.sim_health),   V.sim_health >= 1 ? '정상' : '끊김');\nnode('n-bridge',    fail(V.bridge_fail), V.bridge_fail > 0.01 ? '전송실패' : '정상');\nnode('n-kafka',     up(V.kafka_up),     V.kafka_up >= 1 ? '정상' : '중단');\nnode('n-streams',   stt(V.streams_state), V.streams_state >= 2 ? '정상' : (V.streams_state >= 1 ? '시작중' : '다운'));\nnode('n-dbsink',    up(V.dbsink_db),    V.dbsink_db >= 1 ? '정상' : '끊김');\nnode('n-timescale', up(V.dbsink_db),    V.dbsink_db >= 1 ? '연결됨' : '끊김');\nnode('n-wsserver',  up(V.ws_up),        V.ws_up >= 1 ? '정상' : '중단');\nedge('a-sim',    null,       up(V.sim_health),   null);\nedge('a-bridge', null,       fail(V.bridge_fail), null);\nedge('a-kafka',  'l-kafka',  lagc(V.streams_lag), V.streams_lag);\nedge('a-dbsink', 'l-dbsink', lagc(V.dbsink_lag),  V.dbsink_lag);\nedge('a-ts',     null,       up(V.dbsink_db),     null);\nedge('a-ws',     'l-ws',     lagc(V.ws_lag),      V.ws_lag);\nedge('a-br',     null,       'ok',                null);\n",
        "wrap": true
      }
